reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Organizational Bliss with Unmatched Durability
reviews.reviewText: I am thrilled with the Mangoo Shockproof Carrying Case—a dream for anyone who loves organization! This case not only excels in providing a dedicated space for everything but also boasts impressive durability. Its shockproof design ensures the safety of my belongings, making it an ideal companion for travel or daily use. The thoughtful organization features, coupled with the sturdy construction, make the Mangoo Shockproof Carrying Case an indispensable accessory. If you appreciate both functionality and durability, this case is a must-have for keeping your essentials in order.

reviews.reviewText: I love this case. It fits my portable charger and and a few or the charging cords perfectly. It has a zipper so nothing can come out and its a hard case. Its about the size of an Iphone 11

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars DOLLAR STORE QUALITY
reviews.reviewText: Not a 5 star product by any stretch of the imagination, more like a 1 or 0 star but people don’t pay attention to those, so here we are. This is something you find at the Dollar Store, so save your money because while it’s only $10, it’s not worth more than a buck. Product dimensions are 7” x 3.25”, so smaller than stated in the description. It’s cheaply made and was squished when delivered. It fit my 3’ cord with plug, a 5’ cord and a slim short battery that didn’t encroach on the plug, so not very much. Worst part is the strong toxic odor. Maybe it can be aired out but it’s getting returned because the smell is overwhelming.
